---
title: Vegan Spicy Black Bean & Corn Taquitos with Creamy Guacamole & Pico de Gallo
description: These vegan taquitos are so packed with flavor, you won’t miss the meat! You’ll roll up tortillas with a spicy corn and black bean filling, and while the taquitos bake, you’ll make two toppings—quick homemade pico de gallo and creamy lime-infused guacamole—to take this meal to the next level.
